item.title: Work
item.description: 🏢 Leidos 📍 Morgantown, WV 💼 Software Engineer Intern 🕐 2021-Present Currently still employed at this location. 🏢 Genesis Youth Crisis Center 📍 Clarksburg, WV 💼 Mobile Application Developer 🕐 2020-2021 Developed mobile application in ReactNative to provide resources to youth and families who are currently experiencing an emotional or behavioral crisis on both iOS and Android devices. Designed user interface and graphics to make certain that crisis resources are easily accessible to all users.
